<h1>mkfriend(1): Learn about your coworkers</h1>

<p>How well do you know the thoughtbottles? Can you match 10 in a row to their
avatar? Start the game to find out!</p>

<%= form_for @game do |form| %>
  <p>
    <strong>If you select a cohort</strong>, you won't be quizzed on that cohort's employees.
    For example, if you work in Boston, you might want to select Boston.
  </p>
  <%= form.label :excluded_cohort, "cohort to exclude" %>
  <%= form.collection_select :excluded_cohort, @cohorts, :to_s, :to_s, include_blank: "Test me on EVERY cohort" %>
  <%= form.submit 'Start' %>
<% end %>
